1. *Muzika* je najvažniji deo svake proslave. (Music is the most important part of every celebration.)

2. Oni su slušali *muziku* pre nego što su počeli da vežbaju. (They were listening to music before they started to exercise.)

3. Ona je pohađala časove *muzike* otkad je imala četiri godine. (She has been attending music classes since she was four years old.)

4. On često sluša *muziku* kada je smušen. (He often listens to music when he's feeling down.)

5. *Muzičari* su svirali dok su ljudi plesali. (The musicians were playing while people were dancing.)